OL,5, The recruitment of nurses by           
OL,6, high-income countries from poorer      
OL,7, nations is "out of control", according 
OL,8, to the head of one of the world's      
OL,9, biggest nursing groups.                
OL,11,FThe comments come as the BBC finds     
OL,12,Fevidence of how Ghana's health system  
OL,13,Fis struggling due to the "brain-drain".
OL,15,FMany specialist nurses have left the   
OL,16,FWest African country for better paid   
OL,17,Fjobs overseas.                         
OL,19,FIn 2022 more than 1,200 Ghanaian nurses
OL,20,Fjoined the UK's nursing register.      
